Package com.immunet.immunet.model

Class Pet

java.lang.Object
com.immunet.immunet.model.Pet
public class Pet extends Object
Represents a pet, containing details such as name, date of birth, gender, species, and ownership. This class is responsible for managing the pet's lifecycle, including saving and loading its details through a PetService.

      public boolean isPersisted()
      Determines if the pet's information is persisted in the database.
      Returns:
